</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="7FA6FE7672C1515789254951E7B1B415" pageId="null" pageNumber="350" type="description">
<paragraph id="C1B3BC4AD317238DD83FDAF5B5E47F1D" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="40E4719F04DAA15BF43B2637088CC98F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caprifoliaceae" genus="Knautia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Dipsacales" pageId="null" pageNumber="350" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longifolia">
<emphasis id="D7ACC708D1AA1662E462257FE94DF2AE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">K. longifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 7) durch folgende Merkmale: Pflanze meist kleiner; Stengel unten immer kahl, im obern Teil meist ohne 
<normalizedToken id="40509523ED33C6C40935E6D7DA98F47D" originalValue="Drüsenhaaren" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Druesenhaaren</normalizedToken>
; Blattstiel nicht 
<normalizedToken id="085BE89074183F11D6176FFB9180696A" originalValue="geflügelt" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">gefluegelt</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="C0F2C5D1B8B57AAAAD5DCD50A641A91A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
Blattspreiten oft 
<normalizedToken id="E2DE8AAC47A81BF69A4121908B023CDF" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
; 
<normalizedToken id="10861D0893622E33CB99C237B1B0ACB7" originalValue="Blütenköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Bluetenkoepfe</normalizedToken>
2,5
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="BB36714CA3376CBE81432AD94B132DD5" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
3,5 cm im Durchmesser; 
<normalizedToken id="B47154BC77AED81A95A4D80372710C12" originalValue="äußere" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">aeussere</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="DF1AD25E92FF7510EBBAE847EA5DBFDA" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="07B8FB6039FE6EB6D186B898C87F825E" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="E63A560A8EF87835D5EB8F198F88DA1E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
bis fast so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="6ED6B8B69D29378CA834CDF53F930A24" originalValue="Blüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Blueten</normalizedToken>
, 2
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="E301E056C8CFB6C956DF15FED6998682" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">3</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="869AA483DD1B555AAA6D370A93D590D6" originalValue="½" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">1/2</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="78C045261E687772683DCA611226E7FC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">mal so lang wie breit</emphasis>
, mit weniger zahlreichen Haaren; 
<emphasis id="F2EDF0235C873DB400CBD9B0F6D80630" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Kelchborsten 1,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="1C5247AAFE01E3928BCD034C835FC136" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">2 mm lang.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="B28D640962AAFF16FC0222C2D1EC405D" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0433862AC8DAC10523B7A2F9E5EA2470" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
<emphasis id="1CC47219162780897A55456302C66DDA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="8D0D3335817F51E292745807EC9625A9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">20:</emphasis>
Material aus der Auvergne (Sintes und Cauderon 1965, Sintes 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="EE08DDEE21F423BED7460A5DCF7C0E22" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
<emphasis id="17B6BD37D29EE33C776ECF4A8BDFA811" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin, selten kollin. Feuchte, kalkhaltige, magere 
<normalizedToken id="08963C01B15C72B95A6F80AC0ED1AA1D" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Feuchte Wiesen, Moorwiesen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A5A3C574BB6FD3EC9D5F474A2F459FB1" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">
<emphasis id="CE01C8B3B015C1F65A94202541DBC550" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Verbreitung. Jura-Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="B8CF07626EBB1C5B6F58365F367A6065" originalValue="Östliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">Oestliches</normalizedToken>
Plateau Central, Hochvogesen, Jura. - Im Gebiet: Hochvogesen, Jura (
<normalizedToken id="36B2583B7B69F01B89F12F4F9BF6C0DA" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="350">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Franches Montagnes).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
